title: I Brought a Potato Through Customs, and Now We'll All Die!
info:
My 16K executable music entry from Solskogen 2009, july 17-19. 

Came in 2nd of only 4 entries in the combined compo of 16k-exe and oldschool music, which was won by LoadError.

Music: Punqtured / Fnuque
Synth: Revival / Fnuque

Created using Renoise and the "null_drei"-softsynth. Packed using Crinkler by Blueberry & Mentor. 

Size of executable: 16315 bytes.
Number of instruments: 11
Number of unique tracks: 89
